  "title": "Sales Engineer (Electrical)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Implement sales strategies to expand the customer and distributor network within the designated territory</li>\n  <li>Engage with consultants, contractors, and visit project sites to showcase products and create business opportunities</li>\n  <li>Organize and deliver product training sessions and technical presentations on a regular basis</li>\n  <li>Offer technical assistance to clients and partners both before and after the sale</li>\n  <li>Track market developments, gather customer insights, and observe competitor actions</li>\n  <li>Compile and present sales updates, projections, and activity reports as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of sales experience in Electrical Installation Industry</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation and presentation skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
